1949;;The Man in Black;;British;;Francis Searle;;Betty Ann Davies, Sheila Burrell;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Man_in_Black_(film);;After the death of her yogi father during a freak "yoga accident", Joan Clavering returns home to her widowed and suddenly very wealthy step-mother Bertha. The latter conspires with her daughter Janice to drive Joan insane and deprive her of her rightful inheritance.[4][5][6]